{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_050.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I've been thinking this for a while now, but Linca, your clothes are very lovely!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I really like your fashion sense!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, this? These clothes were bought and given to me by Marion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I just followed her to the tailor and stood in the fitting room."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I-I see. So your clothes are based on Marion's fashion sense..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I do not like these clothes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Why not...?<CR>You look so good in them..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "They are so frilly, they are not suitable for battle. And they rip easily."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it does seem like it'll be tough to patch the ripped areas. The cloth is so thin, you could tell it was patched up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "When they rip, I throw them away. Every month, at least 10 more sets of the same clothes get sent from our home country."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "That many?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Marion is the one who buys them. She tells me to \"dress up, doll up.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x168,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I have even had a dream where Marion was holding lots of clothes, chasing me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Umm, so Linca, does that mean you don't like to dress up...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I do not. I would rather be naked than dress up in clothes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xb,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "If at least this part was made of chain mail, I am sure I would have more fun wearing it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "But, still, I'm sure Marion wants you to look cute."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I am a bodyguard, so I think I should wear clothes suitable for a bodyguard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I guess I can see your point as well, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "(I understand Marion's point of view, too. Linca looks so good in a lovely clothes like these...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "In any event, this is the last set for this month. If it rips, I will not have any more clothes to wear."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I need to be very careful not to rip it... I guess this is also an effective training tool."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Could that be Marion's true intentions?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "It is true that if you wrap yourself in hard armor, your defensive awareness will stagnate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I-I'm not so sure about that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Either way, please do not worry. I will not take my duty of being your bodyguard lightly."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I will do my best to carry out my duty to the end, even if I must be naked to do so!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat? You don't have to go that far. I'm very thankful, but please take better care of your clothes!"
        }
    ]
}